      <title>私募股权对最具风险的有争议贷款类型踩刹车</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/private-equity-hits-the-brakes-on-riskiest-types-of-nav-loans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[多年来，收购公司一直利用有争议的股权支持贷款来提高基金收益。在受到一些原本应该从这种做法中受益的投资者的批评后，它们开始踩刹车。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/private-equity-hits-the-brakes-on-riskiest-types-of-nav-loans</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 16:19:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
